<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jack Karlsson | Portfolio - Game Developer & Software Engineer</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Portfolio of Jack Karlsson, a software engineer specializing in game development (Unity, C#, Unreal Engine) and interactive software.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="Jack Karlsson, Portfolio, Game Developer, Software Engineer, Unity, C#, Unreal Engine, WebGL, Lake Legends, Landing Party">
    <meta name="author" content="Jack Karlsson">

    <!-- Open Graph / Facebook -->
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://jackkarlsson.com">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Jack Karlsson | Portfolio - Game Developer & Software Engineer">
    <meta property="og:description" content="I build games and interactive software. Explore my projects and experience in game development and software engineering.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://jackkarlsson.com/images/lake-legends/lake-legends-splash.png">

    <!-- Twitter -->
    <meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta property="twitter:url" content="https://jackkarlsson.com">
    <meta property="twitter:title" content="Jack Karlsson | Portfolio - Game Developer & Software Engineer">
    <meta property="twitter:description" content="I build games and interactive software. Explore my projects and experience in game development and software engineering.">
    <meta property="twitter:image" content="https://jackkarlsson.com/images/lake-legends/lake-legends-splash.png">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="images/icons/favicon.png?v=1">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="js/theme.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<nav aria-label="Main Navigation">
    <div class="nav-left">
        <a class="nav-element" href="">Home</a>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-right">
        <a class="nav-element" href="#projects"> Projects</a>
        <a class="nav-element" href="#contact">Contact</a>
        <a class="nav-element" href="https://github.com/jackoberto" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        <a class="nav-element" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jackkarlsson/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        <button id="theme-toggle" class="theme-toggle" aria-label="Toggle dark mode">
            <span class="moon-icon">🌙</span>
            <span class="sun-icon">☀️</span>
        </button>
    </div>
</nav>
<header class="center-content">
    <h1>Hi, I'm Jack</h1>
    <p>I build games and interactive software.</p>
    <a id="view-projects" class="nav-element" href="#projects"> View projects</a>
    <a id="contact-me" class="nav-element" href="#contact">Contact me</a>
</header>
<main class="content">
    <section id="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
        <h2 id="about-heading" class="center-content">About</h2>
        <p>
            I’m a software engineer specializing in game development and interactive software. I currently work at <a href="https://www.pley.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pley</a> as a porting engineer and game developer, where I focus on bringing mobile games to the web using WebGL.

            I’m also the co-founder and Lead Developer at <a href="https://www.bridgegamesstudio.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bridge Games Studio</a>, where we are developing the mobile fishing game <a href="projects/lake-legends/">Lake Legends</a>.

            My experience spans a range of technologies including <b>C#</b>, <b>Unity</b>, <b>Unreal Engine</b>, <b>GitHub Actions</b>, and <b>Unity AR Foundation</b> (<b>ARCore</b> and <b>ARKit</b>), as well as porting mobile games to <b>WebGL</b>.

            I have over <b>7 years</b> of experience in software development and a background in game design and programming. I’m an alumni of <b>Forsbergsskola</b>, where I studied Game Programming.
        </p>
    </section>
    <section id="projects" aria-labelledby="projects-heading">
        <h2 id="projects-heading" class="center-content">Projects</h2>
        <section class="grid-container">
            {% for project in projects %}
            <div class="project-container">
                <a href="projects/{{ project.id }}/">
                    <h3 class="project-title">{{ project.title }}: {{ project.subTitle }}</h3>
                    <img class="project-image" src="{{ project.splashScreen }}" alt="{{ project.title }}" />
                    <span class="project-cta">View Project</span>
                </a>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </section>
    </section>
</main>
<section class="contact" id="contact" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
    <h2 id="contact-heading">Contact</h2>
    <p><a href="mailto:jackoberto01@gmail.com">jackoberto01@gmail.com</a></p>
    <p><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jackkarlsson/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></p>
</section>
</body>
</html>